thread.title: Oliver Boxtel
thread.title_full: Store DJ reviewed by Oliver Boxtel

author: Oliver Boxtel
title: Oliver Boxtel
text: I have used Store DJ for years now and have always been more than satisfied with the result. They are quick to call if there are any issues, the delivery time is always really good and they are, in my opinion, the most reasonably priced source of A/V and studio equipment in Australia. Big ups to the guys at Store DJ and keep doing what you're doing!
